name: andrew barrie
what_you_do: Business coaching practice helping business owners, entrepreneurs, and sales professionals improve their sales and business results through synergistic coaching partnerships.
business_focus: Assisting business owners, entrepreneurs, and sales professionals to grow their businesses and improve their quality of life through private coaching.
who_you_serve: Small business owners, executives, financial professionals, entrepreneurs, and salespeople.
social_proof: Andrew has been honored as a Master Certified Coach by the International Coach Federation. He has coached thousands of clients, including many multi-millionaires and prominent business leaders.

bio: Andrew Barber-Starkey is the founder of the ProCoach Success System and has been coaching for over 30 years. In 1999, the International Coach Federation honoured him with the Master Certified Coach designation. He has coached thousands of small business owners, executives, financial professionals and salespeople to achieve their goals.
